            <description><![CDATA[邦威这是疯了吗！【79】就能到手2双帆布鞋<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>【拍2件79】到手美特斯邦威 帆布鞋2双 <br> <br>估计这是新款冲量吧，毕竟线下的话怎么也得七八十一双啊<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>这种一般很快就会抢断码，想入手的姐妹可要抓紧了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <br> <br>ps：这个活动是没有U险的，避免到时候码数什么的不合适要退换，拍的时候建议勾一个U险 <img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me59bzcj20j60j6jsb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me5qoo5j20j60j6wfj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me684mlj20j60j6my4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me6p1p9j20j60j6q4a.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me763uij20j60j6myl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me7mbxsj20j60j6dhk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me83y5vj20j60j6aac.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me8s5ygj20j60j6q3m.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h09me98kktj20j60j63z8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
